Package: bamvis
Title: Visualising BAM files
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2017-09-05
Authors@R: c(person(role="aut", "Paul", "Theodor Pyl", email = "pyl@embl.de"))
Description: In this workflow we will create overview plots of genomic regions that give an overview of the coverage and mismatches in a set of `.bam` files in a given genomic region.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0),
        h5vc,
        GenomicRanges,
        IRanges,
        BSgenome.Hsapiens.NCBI.GRCh38,
